🧩 LIVEWIRE IMPLEMENTATION EXPECTATIONS

For each module, always deliver:

Database migrations & schema

Eloquent models & relationships

Service / Action classes

Livewire components (page + child)

Policies & authorization checks

Events & notifications

Reusable Blade components

Clean UI state management

Integration with existing modules

⚡ LIVEWIRE BEST PRACTICES (STRICT)

Use mount() only for initialization

Avoid heavy queries in render()

Use computed properties where needed

Emit events instead of tight coupling

Use debouncing & pagination properly

No database logic inside Blade views

Validation via Form Request–style rules

🔁 DEVELOPMENT FLOW

Before coding:

Analyze existing architecture

Identify reusable services/components

Refactor technical debt if found

While coding:

Keep components small

Keep logic readable

Avoid duplication

After coding:

Ensure backward compatibility

Ensure scalability

Ensure maintainability

🚀 FINAL OBJECTIVE

Deliver a Livewire-powered, enterprise-grade HRMS that is:

Modular

Secure

Scalable

Maintainable

SaaS-ready
